                <rule id="6291-23e4-e76c-bae1" name="•Overwhelming Volley (Mobile Bay)" publicationId="a53b-cebe-de49-bcbc" hidden="false">
                  <description>If the MOBILE BAY uses its Rate of Fire against an enemy ship, add +2 Nerve tokens to the total when determining how many Nerve tokens are placed on the enemy ship.</description>
